Class VehicleData.Builder

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.objects.vehicle.VehicleData.Builder
Enclosing class:
VehicleData
public static class VehicleData.Builder extends Object
A builder for creating VehicleData objects without using the monstrous constructor.
